            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1359763380,
            "creation_date": 1359763380,
            "body": "<p>Following on from duffymo, the string you want to use is <code>jdbc:mysql://blablabla.rds.amazonaws.com/dbname?user=user&amp;password=password<\/code> as documented <a href=\"http://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.0/en/connector-j-reference-configuration-properties.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">here<\/a><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 14657105,
